<title>BELGIUM: EU Commission vets Daewoo/Thomson merger.</title>
<headline>EU Commission vets Daewoo/Thomson merger.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1996-11-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>The European Commission said on Monday it was reviewing plans by South Korea's Daewoo Electronics Co Ltd to acquire control of Thomson Multimedia, a unit of French consumer electronics company Thomson SA.</p>
<p>The Commission said in a statement the link-up appeared to fall under the merger regulation.</p>
<p>It has one month to decide whether to clear the deal or to open an in-depth investigation into whether it would impede competition on the EU market.</p>
</text>
